  <summary>Live-streams your webcam with HTML overlays</summary>
  <description>
      <p>
          The GstWPEBroadcast demo application allows the live video input (webcam) to
          be mixed with the contents of a web page and streamed to an RTMP
          end-point (Twitch, Youtube,...) which
          can be configured in the settings.
      </p>
